# Backend README (`backend/README.md`)

## Vet Chatbot Backend

This is the **backend (server)** for the Vet Chatbot.
It is built using **Node.js, Express, and MongoDB**.

The backend:

- Handles chat messages
- Stores appointments
- Connects to MongoDB
- Provides APIs for frontend and SDK

---

## Technologies Used

- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB (Mongoose)
- dotenv
- CORS

---

